%% ML Metadata (MLMD) - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as DSP API Server<br/>(Pipeline Controller)
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DB as MySQL/MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Metadata Recording

    DSP->>MLMD: PutExecutionType(request)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, 8080/TCP<br/>Encryption: Configurable (plaintext/TLS)
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE execution_type<br/>MySQL protocol, 3306/TCP<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    DB-->>MLMD: OK
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutExecutionTypeResponse(type_id)

    DSP->>MLMD: PutExecution(request)<br/>with artifacts, events, contexts
    MLMD->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT execution
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT artifacts
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT events (input/output links)
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT attributions & associations
    MLMD->>DB: COMMIT
    DB-->>MLMD: OK
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutExecutionResponse(execution_id, artifact_ids)

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 2: Pipeline Lineage Query

    DSP->>MLMD: GetLineageSubgraph(request)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, 8080/TCP
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT artifacts, executions,<br/>events, contexts (graph traversal)<br/>MySQL protocol, 3306/TCP
    DB-->>MLMD: Result set (lineage data)
    MLMD-->>DSP: GetLineageSubgraphResponse<br/>(artifacts, executions, events, contexts)

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 3: Artifact Retrieval by Context

    DSP->>MLMD: GetArtifactsByContext(context_id)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, 8080/TCP
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT artifacts<br/>JOIN attributions<br/>WHERE context_id = ?
    DB-->>MLMD: Artifact records
    MLMD-->>DSP: GetArtifactsByContextResponse<br/>(artifacts list)
